{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"508","heading":"Assistance for certain youth and charitable organizations","label":"508 Assistance for certain youth and charitable organizations","identifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t32/ch5","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft32%2Fs508","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Change of NameReferences to the United States Olympic Committee deemed to refer to the United States Olympic and Paralympic Committee, see , Patriotic and National Observances, Ceremonies, and Organizations.section 220502(c) of Title 36"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Authority To Provide Services","label":"a .—Authority To Provide Services","identifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft32%2Fs508%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft32%2Fs508%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the provision of such services does not adversely affect the quality of that training or otherwise interfere with the ability of a member or unit of the National Guard to perform the military functions of the member or unit;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft32%2Fs508%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the services to be provided are not commercially available, or any commercial entity that would otherwise provide such services has approved, in writing, the provision of such services by the National Guard;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft32%2Fs508%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"National Guard personnel will enhance their military skills as a result of providing such services; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft32%2Fs508%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the provision of the services will not result in a significant increase in the cost of the training.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Authorized Services","label":"b .—Authorized Services","identifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft32%2Fs508%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t32/s508/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft32%2Fs508%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Ground transportation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/